snippet: The New England Patriots made two big personnel moves on Tuesday when it sent Pro Bowl defensive end Chandler Jones to the Arizona Cardinals in exchange for offensive guard Jonathan Cooper and signed Chris Long....
lead_paragraph: The New England Patriots made two big personnel moves on Tuesday when it sent Pro Bowl defensive end Chandler Jones to the Arizona Cardinals in exchange for offensive guard Jonathan Cooper and signed Chris Long.

headline.main: Pats Trade Away Jones, Bring in Cooper and Long
headline.print_headline: Pats Trade Away Jones, Bring in Cooper and Long
